Long serving local educator, Willem Opperman has been appointed principal of Laerskool Ivypark with effect from 1 January.
Opperman who joined the school in 2006 has been the deputy principal since 2018. Before that he was an educator at Laerskool Chris Hofmeyr.
He said he was grateful for the opportunity and looking forward to working with the circuit managers, educators, parents, learners, School Governing Body and all other stakeholders.
